import { AppBar,Toolbar,IconButton } from "@mui/material"
import {MenuIcon} from '@mui/material'


const HeaderMobile = () => {
  return (
    <AppBar>
        <Toolbar>
        <IconButton>
            <MenuIcon/>
        </IconButton>
        </Toolbar>
    </AppBar>
  )
}

export default HeaderMobile
